<br>
Certain mages need to realize this isn't so much of a nerf on our spell, not nearly as much as it is/would be to a chanter.  This would effectivly reduce the enchanter's charm/solo'ing (Mass AA'ing), to a much more managable level, it would effectivly lower the DPS output of the charmed mobs by roughly 35%.  <br>
<br>
Even with that, the chanter can still slow the &quot;target&quot; mob to still kill 2 rather tough opponents at once for still incredible xp, thus not completely ruining their ability just toning it down a tad.<br>
<br>
Instead of an aa every 20-30 minutes, they will be able to obtain an aa every 35-45 minutes, not a huge change when you think about it.<br>
<br>
To complain is to say &quot;damnit we need to be overpowered because we are xxclass, gimmie gimmie CH, gimmie gimmie 150%rez&quot; there is a place for those it's The DR.........<br>
<br>
Adding roughly 15 minutes to the time it takes 1 class to get an aa, is hardly enough to get upset about, when that 15 minutes added nearly cuts their overall aa/time in half.  This would bring them closer to other classes, while still allowing them DESCENT aa pharming ability.  Also, instead of outdamaging an entire group, they would only be able to outdamage 4 characters of a 6 man (or woman) group.  Hardly even a nerf.  More inline with risk-vs-reward, yes.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thoorne>thoorne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#333333>(1/14/03 3:28:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=408.topic&index=36>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://metacarpes.free.fr/images/thoornehead.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Kinda stupid ...</span><hr size=1> Well, mages got Malosinia. So the resist adjust change isn't that bad. The process will remain the same. Pull will malosinia, mezz, charm, kill, rinse, repeat. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=156959">Thoorne Darkmagi</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
